en_574133_0	Colombo (News1st): The police have launched an investigation into the the abduction of a 17-year old girl from the Mamadala area in Walewatta, Ambalantota.
en_574133_1	According to the Police Media Spokesperson’s Office, the girl was abducted earlier today when a group of six armed men stormed her house.
en_574133_2	Police state that the perpetrators have been identified.
en_574133_3	It has also been revealed that the girl in question was romantically involved with a youth.
en_574133_4	The police believe that he had ochestrated the abduction.
